for aws and azure machines

ssh-copy-id may not work..

pls copy the public key to the client machines profiles

copy the public key from id_rsa.pub from Jenkins master to the /home/<username>/.ssh/authorized_keys file

For AWS Machines

ssh-add ~/.ssh/ec2-keypair (Alternate command if ssh-copy-id  doesn't work on AWS servers


